  "rationale": "Remote is an all-light SaaS brand, so every section sits on a light surface and only the hero carries the single reserved accent on its display heading. Order sells the message in the brand's own vocabulary: a light noise-art hero pairs the 'Everything in one place' headline with the globe illustration and the filled-blue primary pill plus a secondary action; a logo marquee delivers the '10,000+ teams' proof with real customer vectors; a 3-up feature card row renders each value_prop as its own module with a real product card image; a single testimonial stack carries the quote; a compact inline CTA banner is the conversion beat; a lightweight link+legal footer closes. All sections reuse/adapt captured project patterns with disciplined on-grid alignment (offGridExpansion locked) \u2014 the cta section drops the panel-on-media treatment and stays a plain aligned stack per the repair."
